title: 043 - The Return Of The Boobz Brothers
description: On today's show, the guys discuss the SpaceX/Nasa launch that was canceled due to inclement weather, and vent some of their frustrations as they watched the entire 4 hour production leading up the launch. They also answer a few questions, do a little fact checking, and check in with their Australian correspondents, The Boobz Brothers. Keep sending in questions to @ThePodPMI on twitter and instagram, and have a good weekend. Enjoy.
